MOVIE RECOMMENDATION SYSTEM
A simple and interactive Movie Recommendation System built using Random Forest, Streamlit, and developed in PyCharm. This app recommends 5 similar movies based on a movie selected by the user.


Features

 Recommends top 5 similar movies using content-based filtering.
 Uses Random Forest Classifier for modeling.
 Built with Streamlit for a responsive and easy-to-use UI.
 Developed and tested using PyCharm IDE.



How It Works

1. Movie features (like genre, actors, keywords, etc.) are extracted.
2. A Random Forest model learns the similarity between movies.
3. Given a movie title, the app finds 5 most similar movies based on learned features.





